  ('The Coalwood Way','Homer H. Hickam','Biography & Autobiography','Continuing the story of the Rocket Boys of Coalwood, West Virginia, the author recounts his senior year in high school, while the forces of change bring Coalwood to a difficult crossroads and strain threatens to tear apart the Hickam home.',4.13,750),
