  ('A Tear and a Smile','Kahlil Gibran','Philosophy','Contains 56 parables, stories, and poems in Gibran\'s wholly inimitable manner. Illustrated with 4 of his own paintings and drawings, it is the most important edition to the canon of this great writer.',4.03,700),
